summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of EngiPrep PH MVP. All core features are functional - quiz flow, navigation, dark mode, progress tracking working correctly. Test script selector issues caused some false failures, but app functionality is solid.

All 3 subject cards display correctly (Math & Survey, Hydraulics & Geotech, Structural & Construction)
Navigation to Subjects page works correctly
Subject detail pages show topics with lesson and quiz buttons
Complete quiz flow: setup → questions → answers → results
Quiz results page shows percentage, try again and review options
Dark mode toggle works correctly in settings
Settings page loads with all sections (appearance, data management, about)
Progress page displays all stats correctly
Mobile navigation is present and partially functional
Desktop header navigation works for all sections
Progress tracking persists after quiz completion (7% progress, 1 quiz taken, 60% accuracy)
Exam countdown timer shows correct target date (March 2026)
success_percentage: Frontend: 90% - All major features working correctly. Minor selector issues in test scripts don't affect actual functionality.
